			<span class="otherdetails" id="comment_otherdetails_64377554">		
		on Monday April 08, 2024 @03:23AM (<span class="ind"></span><a href="//news.slashdot.org/comments.pl?sid=23283186&amp;cid=64377554">#64377554</a>)
		<small><a href="http://web.lemuria.org/" title="http://web.lemuria.org/" class="user_homepage_display">Homepage</a>
