		<div class="title">
			<h4><a id="comment_link_64377656" name="comment_link_64377656" href="//news.slashdot.org/comments.pl?sid=23283186&amp;cid=64377656" onclick="return D2.setFocusComment(64377656)" >Competence concerns</a>


